2) [u]The Interview: Ramin Jahanbegloo[/u]

Iranian-Canadian Philosophy professor Ramin Jahanbegloo on his imprisonment at Iran's notorious Evin Prison ... and his hopes for a peaceful future in one of the Mideast's most important countries.

[b]Ramin Jahanbegloo[/b] is a professor of Political Science and a Research Fellow in the Centre for Ethics at University of Toronto.

